snippet.textDisplay:
Shukriya to you too, for the incredible and indeed the magical journey of these last few months. The stories you told were essential and inspiring in so many ways. 

One, that we can tell these stories too. Second, that we have such diversity of thought, language, colours, music and life in general. And finally, on a deeper and more profound level, what we as a people can be and where we as can go. Open, welcoming, progressive, innovative and moving forward together as one. 

A vision of Pakistan that is feels like a dream now but a dream worth aspiring towards, worth fighting for.

And in that continuation, there couldn't have been a better song and a better thought to leave us.
تم بھی ہم ہی ہو
ہم بھی تم ہی ہیں"۔

(You are me and I am you. We are one).

Untill me meet again.....
